      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "ふむふむ……。ヒロインはトラウマを抱えているけれど\nとても行動力があるんですね",
      "startTime": 170.4244174007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
